h3. Summary

When you click on *Issues* the following entry is added to the logs:

{noformat}
2016-04-07 15:32:16,377 http-nio-8080-exec-25 WARN pcora 932x269x1 1cozpr3 0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1 /rest/api/1.0/menus/find_link [c.a.j.i.search.util.SearchPropertiesManager] Invalid filter ID in user preferences:
{noformat}

